org.matsim.contrib.analysis.vsp.qgis

Class QGisRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.analysis.vsp.qgis.QGisRenderer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GraduatedSymbolRenderer, QGisRasterRenderer, RuleBasedRenderer, SimpleNetworkRenderer

    public abstract class QGisRenderer
extends Object
    This class provides minimum functionality for rendering a qgis symbol layer. Can be extended by use cases that use a singleSymbolRenderer.

    The renderer describes how a layer is to be drawn. It contains 1...n QgisSymbolLayers in which the symbols for the contained geometry are specified (e.g. points as markers with size, color, transparency, ...).

    dhosse
